data-triple-N3.o: "Saxony-Anhalt is a landlocked state of Germany. Its capital is Magdeburg and it is surrounded by the German states of Lower Saxony, Brandenburg, Saxony and Thuringia. Saxony-Anhalt covers an area of 20,447.7 square kilometres . It has a population of 2.34 million. Saxony-Anhalt should not be confused with Saxony or Lower Saxony, also German states."@en
